(Meyl.) Mar. Mey. &amp; Poulain
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation id="131F0BD8FFB0FFF582872F6335F89E71" box="[682,750,266,292]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="8.[136,229,1775,1797]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,821,1750]" captionTargetId="figure-243@8.[151,1436,821,1750]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 4. Physarum nivale a, b. Sporocarp. c. Physaroid capillitium and spores. d. Spores." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6555911" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6555911/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="39">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
